ZH: 我每天早上锻炼半个小时。
EN: I exercise for half an hour every morning.

ZH: 要保持健康身体，就需要定期锻炼。
EN: To maintain a healthy body, regular exercise is necessary.

ZH: 健康饮食和适当的锻炼是保持身体健康的关键。
EN: Healthy eating and proper exercise are key to maintaining a healthy body.

ZH: 我喜欢户外锻炼，感觉更开心。
EN: I enjoy exercising outdoors, it makes me feel happier.

ZH: 锻炼之后，我觉得更精力充沛。
EN: After exercising, I feel more energized.

ZH: 她每天骑自行车来锻炼身体。
EN: She exercises by biking every day.

ZH: 跑步是我最喜欢的锻炼方式。
EN: Running is my favorite way to exercise.

ZH: 在健身房里可以进行各种各样的锻炼。
EN: Various types of exercises can be done at the gym.

ZH: 他每周锻炼三次，保持体型。
EN: He exercises three times a week to keep fit.

ZH: 锻炼可以提高心肺功能。
EN: Exercise can improve cardiovascular function.

ZH: 她最近开始锻炼，但感觉很累。
EN: She recently started exercising, but feels tired.

ZH: 长期不锻炼会导致身体变得虚弱。
EN: Not exercising for a long time can make the body weak.

ZH: 我们每周都会锻炼一次，以保持健康。
EN: We exercise once a week to stay healthy.

ZH: 她从不锻炼，却拥有优美的身材。
EN: She never exercises, yet she has a great figure.

ZH: 在锻炼时要注意保护好自己的身体。
EN: When exercising, be sure to protect your body.

ZH: 在晴天锻炼比在雨天好。
EN: Exercising on a sunny day is better than on a rainy day.

ZH: 锻炼可以帮助缓解压力。
EN: Exercise can help alleviate stress.

ZH: 每天锻炼让我感觉更有活力。
EN: Exercising every day makes me feel more energetic.

ZH: 健康的饮食和适量的锻炼是保持健康的关键。
EN: Healthy eating and moderate exercise are the keys to maintaining good health.
